ARTICLE.TITLE: Cork cage fighter hooks up with wrestler on First Dates
ARTICLE.TEXT:
Cork cage fighter hooks up with wrestler on First Dates

WILL Clodagh, a 22-year-old former cage fighter and call centre operator from Cork, meet her match in wrestling fan Declan, aged 24, from Kildare?

All will be revealed in the next episode of First Dates Ireland on RTE2 on Thursday at 9.30pm.

Also, full-time sales assistant and part-time stripper Josie, 24, of Dublin, compares tattoos with full-time retail manager and part-time barber Gary, aged 28, from Wexford.

And student Mairead, aged 20, from Galway, has to overcome her introverted nature when she meets out-going makeup artist Alex, aged 19, of Leitrim.

All in this week's show, Thursday March 5.
